title: This is why moms (and some dads) are always exhausted
text:
We have to feed a bunch of people, sometimes from our boobs, like multiple times a day. Every. Damn. Day. We answer the question "why" at least 343 times a day. We have to be nice and socialize with other parents we don't like for the sake of our children.
See the full story at Huffington Post
